parameters: Principal: "I can't believe you found this place..."

Principal: "Tch, my plan to extract the secrets from this guy is
ruined..."
Pony-Celes: "You have nowhere left to run."

Hypnogogue: "My name is Hypnogogue, the great hypnotist!"

Hypnogogue: "It is my mission to hypnotize all humans in Japan and
make them swear eternal loyalty to Lord Domudra!"
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘冷たい目

Pony-Celes: "So you were a monster after all. I won't hold back
anymore!"

Hypnogogue: "Kukukuku, this form that Lord Domudra has remodeled me
into is special."
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘冷たい目

Hypnogogue: "These antennas can receive hypnotic waves and emit them
at a super high concentration directly at the target."
Hypnogogue: "No matter who you are, it's impossible to resist."
Hypnogogue: "Pony-Celes, you have no chance of winning!"
Pony-Celes: "So you can't hypnotize without relying on a machine."

Pony-Celes: "And you call yourself a great hypnotist? Aren't you
ashamed?"

Hypnogogue: "To speak so bluntly about what I'm most self-conscious
about..."

Hypnogogue: "It seems you need a thorough punishment for your insolent
tongue."
Hypnogogue: "First, I'll take away the freedom of your arms!"

Hypnogogue: "You will never be able to hit me... never be able to hit
me..."

Pony-Celes: "It's useless, I've destroyed all the hypnotic devices.
Such tricks won't work on Pony-Celes."
Hypnogogue: "Destroyed everything? Are you sure about that?"
Pony-Celes: "The ringing in my ears, the headache is coming back..."

Hypnogogue: "What you destroyed were just mass-produced models that I
created to mimic the original."
Hypnogogue: "It doesn't matter how many of those you destroy."
Pony-Celes: "There's an original? Where on earth could it be..."
Hypnogogue: "Do you think I would tell you that?"

Hypnogogue: "...I would like to say that, but as a reward for finding
this place, I'll give you a little chance."

Hypnogogue: "Now, where do you think the original is? If you can guess
it, I might go easy on you."

Pony-Celes: "A place I would never enter... that's the boys'
restroom!"
Hypnogogue: "As a punishment, I'll make your legs immobile too!"
Hypnogogue: "Look, now you can't walk... can't walk"

Hypnogogue: "What's wrong Pony-Celes? Where did all your bravado
go?"
Pony-Celes: "You hid it somewhere in the gymnasium, didn't you!"
Hypnogogue: "As a punishment, I'll make your legs immobile too!"
Hypnogogue: "Look, now you can't walk... can't walk"

Hypnogogue: "What's wrong Pony-Celes. Where did all your bravado
go?"
Pony-Celes: "I've got it. The place is the sports field!"

Pony-Celes: "The principal, you chose the sports field as the
evacuation site when we were attacked by Zyda!"

Pony-Celes: "You proposed to build an evacuation facility and made
sure no one could enter the sports field, all for this reason."

Hypnogogue: "Seeing my plan being seen through really gets under my
skin."

Hypnogogue: "But... a promise is a promise. I'll go a bit easy on
you."

Pony-Celes: "Even if I can't use my arms, I won't lose to someone
like you! Come at me!"

Hypnogogue: "Fufufu, let's see how long that spirit lasts. Now... here
I come!"
